{"tid":1557474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人要多謝維尼","createTime":"2019-09-10T06:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T07:07:03.000Z","uid":191926,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9d9de493ad9bb2f6486cd81e428961bf520460","tid":1557474,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"其實<br />\n香港依家呢個問題遲早都會出現<br />\n除左少數人 (例如堆愛支那黑警)<br />\n<br />\n根本 語言，文化，價值，生活，制度<br />\n樣樣野都唔同<br />\n矛盾會爆發共實係遲早的事<br />\n<br />\n但早出現好過遲出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼呢一刻 中國仲唔夠美國來<br />\n美國仲可以牽制到中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果中國繼續玩鄧小平<br />\n到胡溫果套韜光養晦  漸步滲透<br />\n10年後會好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港都會被溫水煮蛙整死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n維尼上台後奉行 <br />\n3樣明顯國策<br />\n<br />\n1. 侵略性外交政策<br />\n2. 世界主義 <br />\n3. 極左文革路線<br />\n<br />\n直接後果係維尼任內  <br />\n支共係世界形象急速惡化<br />\n經濟開始不穩<br />\n佢果種以鬥爭為樂   又係得罪人多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以前 香港人反中 <br />\n會被西方報紙  話我地搞歧視<br />\n依家反中 西方形容我地為 <br />\n捍衛民主自由的大衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n鄧小平講過 防右 但主要防左<br />\n係中共呢種黨性 文化  <br />\n極左災難出現頻密<br />\n遠遠大於右派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602289d74690d60e9c45e9ac177c7cd7a4af858c","tid":1557474,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:35:46.000Z","msg":"所以如果換李克強做真係煮撚熟埋<br />\n好彩條撚屌排第二"},{"pid":"d0234d6b4c6970a944fff6ab9bfcff3c5b1b1956","tid":1557474,"uid":166245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:38:41.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">以前 香港人反中\n會被西方報紙 話我地搞歧視\n依家反中 西方形容我地為\n捍衛民主自由的大衛O:-)</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nsad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7f934a1b575c0ab1c2c062830e9bb443567583","tid":1557474,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"大時代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8d74839768116fa0f4862dd7317fa7c861fd3f","tid":1557474,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"某程度上中共無得簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鄧胡個時慢慢發展緊個個都係為左搵2餐甚至更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔會理身邊發生咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到左E家開始穩定落黎會留意番自己身邊個陣 中共就要制造敵人黎收民心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前係日本 E家係美國"}]}